KUBERNETES 
WHAT IS KUBECTL? CLI tool for k8s

How to create a pod?
--- First prpare the yaml file for pod.
    Paste it inside the control plane.
    command--> kubectl create -f <pod name>
    Check for the pod --> kubectl get pods
                          kubectl get pods -o wide (for illustrated information of pod)
    Enter the pod --> minikube ssh
    check running status --> curl <IP Address>
